data.name: richTextBox_Information.Text
data.value:
The import tab let you the interface package to override your personnal settings and addons. The current AddOns folder will bebackuped and replace by the AddOns of the package. The settings for the selected character will be backuped and overrided by the settings in the package.
The export tab will create the package from a specific character. Thus, you will be able to share it with other players or use it as a backup !
Please, be sure to have correctly set the World of Warcraft path in the settings tab.

data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: Welcome on WoWZiport. This program was made to easily import or export a complete interface for a specified character. While importing a new interface, it will automatically create a backup of the orginal interface.
